    • Method Detail

      • getAnswers

        public ArrayList<Answer> getAnswers​(ArrayList<String> intents)
        This method checks if there is a match for the key words from the user's question. If there is a match, an answer is returned. If there is no match, it will tell the user that there is no answer found. Please be aware that there may be multiple matched answers returned to the user.
        Specified by:
        getAnswers in interface KnowledgeBase
        Parameters:
        intents - contains the keywords from the user's question.
        Returns:
        a list of the answers for the user
